@page "/basic"

<div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24">
    <section class="py-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">Basic Image Optimization</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Discover the simplicity of optimizing images with the <code class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 font-mono px-2 py-1 rounded">Image</code> component. This example showcases its fundamental usage with explicitly defined width and height, ensuring automatic optimization and <strong class="font-semibold">lazy loading</strong> by default for improved performance.
        </p>

        <div class="rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden border border-gray-200 max-w-lg mx-auto">
            <div class="relative aspect-w-3 aspect-h-2 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center">
                <Image Src="/images/photo.jpeg"
                       Alt="Example image"
                       DefaultSrc="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2022/02/13/17/22/cartoon-easter-bunny-7011655_1280.jpg"
                       Width="600"
                       Height="400"
                       CssClass="border border-gray-200 p-2 rounded-sm" />
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-green-600 font-semibold">
            The original image size was approximately 1.5 MB, now efficiently optimized to around 71 KB!
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 text-gray-600">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Key Benefits:</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Automatic Optimization:</strong> Images are optimized behind the scenes.</li>
                <li><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-800">WebP Conversion:</strong> Default conversion to the efficient WebP format.</li>
                <li><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Adjustable Quality:</strong> Default quality setting of 75.</li>
                <li><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Layout Stability:</strong> Explicit dimensions prevent content layout shifts.</li>
                <li><strong class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Lazy Loading:</strong> Images load only when they enter the viewport, improving initial page load.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 rounded-md bg-gray-100 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Code Example</h3>
            <pre class="bg-gray-200 rounded-md overflow-x-auto p-4 font-mono text-sm text-gray-900"><code>
&lt;Image
    Src="/example-image.jpg"
    Alt="Example image"
    DefaultSrc="..." &lt;!-- (optional) override error messages --&gt;
    Width="600"
    Height="400" /&gt;
</code></pre>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
